        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         We\xe2\x80\x99re aiming to do two per week, one every Tuesday and Friday. Not Boring Founders is a
         <strong>
          lighter-weight way to help founders tell their story
         </strong>
         than a full Deep Dive, and it\xe2\x80\x99s a great
         <strong>
          touchpoint with founders
         </strong>
         we\xe2\x80\x99ve invested in or would like to invest in.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         I\xe2\x80\x99m not a great interviewer yet, but I\xe2\x80\x99m starting to get more comfortable. We\xe2\x80\x99re going to lean into making the podcast great and growing the audience over the next few months.
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUMtqxDAM_Jr1MfiZOAcfeulvGD-UrGliB1vpkr-vd7e0ICTEoBnNBIewlnqZozQkz2bxOsBkeLQNEKGSs0G1KRo2ci2UnEk0MjKtNEnNLhVgd2kzWE8gx-m3FBymkl8XlHJF7kYsfPFaS-ciZ1PniFypGKRfQhCMy7euO2OCHMDAN9SrZCCbuSMe7SY-bvyzFz7S86MhlL1vuaAvNeU1FJIMp5xTyRjjStJp4MMySa3FPLLog3IUBsnycTHhbpLuKx_a6Ru68PVkI9X8sXX46-522F5Ad2T73M-c8LKQnd8gvs3iO7OXfbtChtqzjNZhT0rOo2bjpAX7NdfTUGxmfBwV6cqx9Kv8L_oDRuWD6g" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Follow Not Boring on Twitter
         </a>
         and share when you hear an episode you like to help us grow it.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         <strong>
          Not Boring Talent Collective
         </strong>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         In practically every investor update email we receive from companies, the #1 ask for investors is always the same:
         <strong>
          HIRING
         </strong>
         .
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         As a solo GP, I wasn\xe2\x80\x99t particularly helpful in this area. Larger funds have teams dedicated to sourcing and hiring talent; I was lucky if I happened to know someone looking who might fit a role. That meant I was often left replying. \xe2\x80\x9cGreat month! Will keep my eye out for anyone who would be a good fit for [x role].\xe2\x80\x9d Which is weak.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Luckily, Not Boring portfolio company
         <strong>
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUMGuhCAM_JrlaAAB8cDhXfY3CEJ1ySIYrM_4949dDy9p2qST6XTGO4Sl1MtsZUfyaRavDUyGc0-ACJUcO1Qbg2GK616KkQQjAtNSk7jbuQKsLiaD9QCyHVOK3mEs-cuglEvyMgK8d2M_qAlADX4Gr6T3XomRhhkGfuu6I0TIHgz8Qr1KBpLMC3HbH_3Pgz9bnefZbS61vzpf1rYg0XDKORWMMS4FHTrezYPQuh8VC5OXjkInWN4u1ruHoOvCu_2YdnT-_TlBqskFp1JjXhr8frkV0hdoTmyb65EjXhaymxKE2yTeWX1t2wUy1JZhsA5bQmJUmqlB90zcploKko2MKyVJUw6lsfK_6B9XwoEk" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
           Pallet
          </a>
         </strong>
         recently rolled out talent collectives, and Dan worked with them to launch the
         <strong>
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMFuhCAQhp9mudUAAuKBQy99DYIwuqQIBsY2vn3Z9dCEAGEy8_F_3iFspV7mKA3Ja7N4HWAy_LYEiFDJ2aDaGAxTXI9SzCQYEZiWmsRm1wqwu5gM1hPIcS4peoex5HcHpVySp-EQZudHoeTqldeLhonzRVE_T6tQQt9cd4YI2YOBH6hXyUCSeSIe7TF-PvhXX7ngx1JqzNtwuNS_N_iy93d0CTL2C4mGU86pYIxxKeg08GGdhNbjrFhYvHQUBsHycbHRPQTdNz60c2no_PdrFqmmM25EL38_3Q7pXejJbD_3M0e8LGS3JAh3aLzdvTXYDTLU7jRYh92YmJVmatIjE3fIbkWymXGlJOnkUHpX_of-AfpahfY" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
           Not Boring Talent Collective
          </a>
         </strong>
         .
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         The Not Boring readership is full of smart, curious people \xe2\x80\x93 people willing to read ~10k words per week \xe2\x80\x93 many of whom are looking for their next thing. So far, we\xe2\x80\x99ve admitted
         <strong>
          over 500
         </strong>
         of you from places like Google, Stripe, Meta, Amazon, Citadel, Peloton, Instacart, and many more top companies\xc2\xa0into the talent collective. Then we give our portfolio companies
         <strong>
          free access.
         </strong>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         <em>
          <strong>
           (If you\xe2\x80\x99re looking for a new job or looking to hire Not Boring people,
           <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMFuhCAQhp9mudUAAuKBQy99DYIwuqQIBsY2vn3Z9dCEAGEy8_F_3iFspV7mKA3Ja7N4HWAy_LYEiFDJ2aDaGAxTXI9SzCQYEZiWmsRm1wqwu5gM1hPIcS4peoex5HcHpVySp-EQZudHoeTqldeLhonzRVE_T6tQQt9cd4YI2YOBH6hXyUCSeSIe7TF-PvhXX7ngx1JqzNtwuNS_N_iy93d0CTL2C4mGU86pYIxxKeg08GGdhNbjrFhYvHQUBsHycbHRPQTdNz60c2no_PdrFqmmM25EL38_3Q7pXejJbD_3M0e8LGS3JAh3aLzdvTXYDTLU7jRYh92YmJVmatIjE3fIbkWymXGlJOnkUHpX_of-AfpahfY" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
            sign up here
