        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         This is exactly the kind of thing I want us to be doing with Dan on board: finding
         <strong>
          scalable ways to help portfolio companies
         </strong>
         by leveraging our unique assets without needing to build out an enormous team to do it. Bonus points if we can use portfolio companies\xe2\x80\x99 products.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         We have a couple of other things in the works, as well:
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
